de.humatic.dsj

Class DSFilterInfo.DSCrossBarInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.humatic.dsj.DSFilterInfo.DSCrossBarInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    DSFilterInfo

    public class DSFilterInfo.DSCrossBarInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    DSCrossBarInfo represents a capture device's crossbar, which is used to hardware-internally connect inputs to outputs on multi analogue IO devices like combined TV / analogue video capture boards. It is constructed internally on device query and can not be constructed by application code.
